Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.91,0:00:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亞少年  魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.35,0:00:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從謎之少女C.C.那裡得到了不可思議的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.49,0:00:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.13,0:00:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠對任何人下達命令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,並讓其絕對遵守的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.72,0:00:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了妹妹娜娜莉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.53,0:00:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修計劃將布里塔尼亞帝國毀滅
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.80,0:00:25.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,另一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.43,0:00:27.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他的好友樞木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.97,0:00:30.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正逐漸在帝國內部確立自己的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,時至此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今後的命運或許已經注定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,395)}STAGE 8
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.66,0:02:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn方正综艺_GBK}{\fad(600,0)\pos(424,430)}黑之騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.87,0:02:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是第一次走出東京租界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:35.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修也來就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.10,0:02:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.73,0:02:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚徹夜長談
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.89,0:02:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和喜歡的男生互訴衷腸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.12,0:02:44.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,會長你有這樣的對象麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.31,0:02:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.91,0:02:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.21,0:02:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[河口湖: 位於山梨縣東南部的富士五湖之一 觀光勝地]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.21,0:02:55.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,河口湖有很多布里塔尼亞觀光客\N治安也很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.95,0:02:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會像貧民區那樣可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.19,0:02:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.12,0:03:01.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.89,0:03:03.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次不會扔下你不管的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.74,0:03:16.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快進來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:21.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從現在開始 這裡就是我們的基地了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.87,0:03:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個… 可以理解為你願意和我們合作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我們是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.50,0:03:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:34.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西你是怎麼弄到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:35.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我拜託了一下 他們就送給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.99,0:03:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向那些只知道吃喝嫖賭的貴族們
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:38.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:40.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼簡單就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不會留下把柄的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:44.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂  還有二樓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:46.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這車子會不會太大了點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:49.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這樣反而可能會成為軍隊盤查的盲點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,連電視都有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現場情況現在怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.17,0:03:54.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是 這裡是河口湖的會議中心酒店(Convention Center Hotel)前方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:04:00.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,劫持酒店的犯人自稱是日本解放戰線
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.46,0:04:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,目前他們把以詹姆斯議長為首的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:06.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[Sakuradite：產於富士山附近的稀有金屬\N確保Sakuradite的供應是布里塔尼亞對日本發動侵略戰爭的原因之一]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.75,0:04:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Sakuradite分配會議的與會人員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和正好在場的觀光客  以及數名工作人員作為人質
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是犯人送來的影像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,除了詹姆斯議長等人以外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:14.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還能看到學生的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:16.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,學生會的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,犯罪集團的首領是自稱草壁中校的舊日本軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:23.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,製造高溫超導體不可或缺的原料Sakuradite
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.48,0:04:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是直接影響到世界安全保障的重要戰略物資
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.46,0:04:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,AREA-11是世界最大的Sakuradite的產地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,佔全世界供給量的70%
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:43.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每年在這裡舉辦的Sakuradite生產國會議
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.58,0:04:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,決定著Sakuradite的國際分配比率
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說其結果就是我們布里塔尼亞\N和其他諸國的國力之比也不為過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖份子很可能正是看準了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,此會議所具有的引發重大國際輿論的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.26,0:05:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才做出這次挾持酒店的暴行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.97,0:05:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是日本解放戰線的草壁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.72,0:05:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是為了日本的獨立解放而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各位雖然不是軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但卻是布里塔尼亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:12.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是妄圖支配我們的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:14.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,若是乖乖聽話就不會傷害你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.80,0:05:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:18.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,開始行動了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:21.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他們可是日本最大的反布里塔尼亞勢力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.96,0:05:23.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自然不甘人後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,針對我們嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:27.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該高興還是該悲傷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他們這樣只會和敵方同歸於盡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,利瓦爾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:34.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是魯魯修
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請在提示音後留言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.12,0:05:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在這種時候他在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.68,0:05:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,連接酒店的橋樑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.26,0:05:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,除主橋外 其他全部被切斷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從上空和水下的接近作戰全部以失敗告終
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下有可能執行人質救出作戰的道路只有一條
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:06:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,延伸至會議中心酒店正下方的供給通道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使用這條通道的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.19,0:06:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按照作戰計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.22,0:06:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以將地基破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使酒店沉入水中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.14,0:06:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個通道是為了運送物資而建造
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:12.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以即使是Sutherland也可以通過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敵方肯定對此有所準備
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但不會有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:18.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,GO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:20.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從以往他們所使用的武器等級來看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:22.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全可以迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發現敵影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和預想一樣  從地下通道進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:27.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[雷光: 由2台改造過的GLASGOW從2側支撐起中間的Linear Cannon的特製KnightMare Frame\NLinear Cannon: 通過電磁誘導射出超高速炮彈的炮台]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.08,0:06:28.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雷光  啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,左右四連腳部固定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[超電磁式榴散彈重炮: 裝備在雷光中的對KnightMare用大型加農炮\N射出的榴散彈可輕易貫通KnightMare裝甲 在限定空間內迴避困難]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,超電磁式榴散彈重炮  電壓確認
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.94,0:06:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,預計會有反KnightMare來福炮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,散開後突破
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.84,0:06:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,超電磁式榴散彈重炮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:44.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發射!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:47.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一擊斃命
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.32,0:06:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,派上用場了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雷光
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,領教了吧 布里塔尼亞的豬頭們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,全滅!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.80,0:06:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人設置了用Glasgow改造的炮台
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:01.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是Linear Cannon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:03.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說突破無望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.02,0:07:06.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按他們要求 釋放政治犯嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:08.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能向恐怖份子示弱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 尤菲米婭殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:15.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,關於這點 應該還未被覺察到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:19.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果他們知道人質中有尤菲米婭殿下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.06,0:07:21.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定會被用來作為交涉籌碼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.66,0:07:23.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為殿下只是作為旁聽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以會議名單上沒有她的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這次一定會順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:37.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 我可不是他的監護人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們特派不能參加人質救出作戰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然申請是提交了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.45,0:07:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但我們是命令系統不同的特殊部門
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能把作戰交給ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.24,0:07:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柯內莉婭殿下是嚴格區分佈裡塔尼亞人和NUMBERS的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.25,0:08:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還無法讓她認同我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.36,0:08:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底為了什麼才建立名譽布里塔尼亞人制度的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:08.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這位父親  你女兒莎莉小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西要放到哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:10.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那裡那裡 駕駛室那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.83,0:08:12.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 放在這裡的箱子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.04,0:08:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她只是去觀光而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.24,0:08:16.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她還只是個學生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,卻被恐怖份子無差別地擄走…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不可原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莎莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.68,0:08:22.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的女兒會平安無事嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子明明什麼壞事都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.18,0:08:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了與布里塔尼亞作戰 組織是必須的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:33.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不能就這麼袖手旁觀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:35.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,按照柯內莉婭的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會無視人質的存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.96,0:08:39.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 為什麼到現在她還按兵不動?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.72,0:08:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.89,0:08:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人質會怎麼樣呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無論怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.92,0:08:49.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都沒有放過布里塔尼亞人的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.65,0:08:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是… 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:55.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個分給大家可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個… 雖然我是覺得很帥啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我們是反抗組織
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們並不是反抗組織
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.50,0:09:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.92,0:09:07.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:10.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正義的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.25,0:09:13.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傳令各特別狙擊小隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.11,0:09:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,維持現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.31,0:09:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各小隊長進行通報確認…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.44,0:09:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人質中的學生… 是學生會的同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交涉還在進行 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是組織的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起個人的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.51,0:09:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我會以組織的規則優先
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:30.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塞希爾小姐  那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:31.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.02,0:09:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道  想把人質…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.48,0:09:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.70,0:09:40.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.58,0:09:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是對我們的要求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:45.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仍然沒有任何回應的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每隔30分鐘我們會推一個人質下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.36,0:09:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了人質 希望你們作出具有誠意的回應
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然殺雞儆猴  那些野蠻人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:57.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不如我們先暫且同意交涉  至少讓他們先放了婦女和孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.52,0:09:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.49,0:10:00.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦我們進行了交涉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:02.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就代表認同了恐怖份子的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:04.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就強攻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.13,0:10:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個應該是在確保了尤菲米婭殿下的安全之後才可以採取的策略吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.52,0:10:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.45,0:10:13.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總督  ZERO…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從ZERO那裡傳來聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.29,0:10:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.41,0:10:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三號車被ZERO給偷走了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.82,0:10:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉姆森在幹什麼啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說是回過神來車子已經被開走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:27.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼現在那輛三號車呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在軍隊的正中間
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.34,0:10:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經確認了  是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.95,0:10:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要實施狙擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,保持現狀 待機
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:37.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,包圍完成後 再逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:41.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  他所說的正義是什麼意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:42.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.85,0:10:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在那之前可能會被殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,後面的同伴也沒有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼不用我們自己那輛車
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:53.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可以在眾目睽睽之下把自己的基地曝光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.91,0:10:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以相信他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:57.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個叫ZERO的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我早說了他很可疑嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過萬一出了什麼事 我會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:08.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柯內莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我很想在這裡回報你上次的招待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.63,0:11:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 現在利用你還是太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.18,0:11:15.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果像預想的一樣 就不需要使用Geass了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又見面了呢 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.33,0:11:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是日本解放戰線的成員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.69,0:11:24.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說想要協助他們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.71,0:11:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在要以處理我們的事優先
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.21,0:11:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,愚弟克洛維斯的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:32.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就讓你在此償還
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,柯內莉婭  你選擇哪一個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.93,0:11:39.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已死的克洛維斯 和 活著的尤菲米婭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好!  果然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:44.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第一個條件已經確認了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是老樣子沒變啊  柯內莉婭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直以來都很溺愛尤菲米婭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你才無法行動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感情束縛了你的手腳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我來救出尤菲米婭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:11:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:02.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對能救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:05.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.97,0:12:07.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,從布里塔尼亞那裡傳來的聯絡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,傳令全軍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.65,0:12:11.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓ZERO通過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,重複
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,讓ZERO通過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.27,0:12:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本解放戰線會把我視為同志來歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.07,0:12:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是當作障礙來清除呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無論如何
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:34.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他們是無法抗拒能與ZERO會面這個誘惑的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:38.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,作戰的前提條件全部確認
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:44.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦  總督
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.97,0:12:46.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由於ZERO的到來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他們殺死下一個人質的時間應該稍有推遲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  這是個好機會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.29,0:12:54.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,連同ZERO一網打盡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:58.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,瞭解 非常感謝您的指名
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:13:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以出擊了 Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說是要從正面突破供給通道的Linear Cannon
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.51,0:13:05.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,羅伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.39,0:13:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這不是說要把我們當成誘餌來製造破綻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  似乎親衛隊將趁機衝進去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎? 怎麼這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.41,0:13:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塞希爾  我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.93,0:13:17.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請讓我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:21.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,既然為了救出大家而需要我和Lancelot的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.95,0:13:22.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我就應該去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.06,0:13:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是作為誘餌也不要緊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:40.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,樞木准尉  現在說明作戰概要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.45,0:13:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,根據精密探測(Prime Search)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人質都被困在酒店的中間層的食品儲藏庫裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嚮導兵器  Z-01  Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.06,0:13:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使用供給通道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.54,0:13:51.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,移動到酒店地下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到達後 破壞酒店的地基
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,使酒店沉入水中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人質所在的地方預計可支撐8分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.40,0:14:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人質的救出及恐怖份子的清除由其他部隊負責
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[VARIS: Variable Ammunition Repulsion Impact Spitfire\N手持來福槍,泛用彈藥斥力衝擊炮,通過Impact Rail的更換可以適應各種戰況\NImpact Rail: VARIS的可換裝部分 通過該部分可發射各種效果的炮彈\N反物質: 與正物質相對應,正反物質在接觸時雙方同時湮滅,釋放出大量能量]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.41,0:14:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,另外為了破壞地基需要使用VARIS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:09.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,衝擊能量設定為反物質(Anti-Material)3級
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.52,0:14:13.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 剩下的問題就是埋伏於隧道內的Linear Cannon了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,由於空間受到限制
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.87,0:14:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以即使是Lancelot  迴避率也只有47.8%
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.21,0:14:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:23.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你要在適當的時機回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.28,0:14:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能把Lancelot弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,適當的時機?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:28.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這個星期天我要和會長還有妮娜去河口湖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.03,0:14:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:39.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 那天我有工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:40.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:45.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 謝謝你邀請我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:47.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.86,0:14:51.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,離作戰開始還有12分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:52.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,進入倒計時
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.84,0:14:56.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,E… ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛才說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然說ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:01.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是日本人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們知道了啦  所以請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.86,0:15:04.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快給我糾正
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.90,0:15:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不是ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會糾正的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:09.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你那算什麼口氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.82,0:15:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們來隔壁房間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:13.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好教育一下你們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:15.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.09,0:15:19.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,給我起來  你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:22.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.00,0:15:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:24.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請讓我和你們的首領見面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.29,0:15:29.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊  副總督
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:33.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是布里塔尼亞第三皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尤菲米婭·Li·布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.74,0:15:39.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:46.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不想和我聯手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.65,0:15:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就讓我們看看你的真面目  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.21,0:15:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣很無禮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在此之前我想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.15,0:15:57.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在此次行動的最後  希望得到怎樣的結果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那還用說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.96,0:16:02.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要讓國內外都知道日本人還沒有死光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:03.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真陳腐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們思想真陳腐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:08.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已經無可救藥了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.68,0:16:09.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是什麼意思  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[M.V.Booster: 搭載於Lancelot上的超高速移動系統\N發動時Lancelot具有比通常狀態更高速的移動性能]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,M.V.Booster
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:16.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Lancelot  出發!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.36,0:16:20.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反應確認
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.31,0:16:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敵方KnightMare  一機
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,移動速度約為普通的兩倍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:25.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係  反正都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.16,0:16:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,超電磁式榴散彈重炮 發射!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:39.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不是說了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他本來就不打算作為誘餌  而是準備好好幹一場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請報告中校
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才聯絡時說的人質帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,自稱是尤菲米婭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.26,0:16:55.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO  我們已經無話可談了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.65,0:16:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:16:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.56,0:17:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.74,0:17:13.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,中校他們已經自行了斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.24,0:17:16.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,覺悟到自己此次的行動毫無意義之後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.08,0:17:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尤菲米婭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:22.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,為了民眾挺身而出嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:23.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是沒變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼  特派的KnightMare
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  照這樣下去似乎可以突破
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以期待嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.96,0:17:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  這程度的破壞力還可以承受
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.81,0:17:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第五發也被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:40.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:41.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要膽怯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[四連腕部自在炮台: 搭載於超電磁式榴散彈重炮的副裝備]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.94,0:17:44.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,四連腕部自在炮台展開
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡可是絕對防衛線 必須死守!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.19,0:17:47.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,塞希爾小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.06,0:17:49.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要在這裡使用VARIS
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.49,0:17:51.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 那太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.72,0:17:54.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可滑行領域已經很窄了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已有承受爆炸衝擊的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們這些傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:08.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說你就任副總督了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尤菲米婭皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.86,0:18:12.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這並非什麼值得高興的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,確實  因為克洛維斯死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是我殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.52,0:18:21.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直到最後他還在向我乞求饒他一命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.00,0:18:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用那張下令殺死ELEVEN的嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你就殺了皇兄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.55,0:18:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.23,0:18:30.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是布里塔尼亞皇帝的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.82,0:18:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.47,0:18:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.13,0:18:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能量全開
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:41.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,炮身被毀也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對要死守到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.11,0:18:45.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,萬歲!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.42,0:19:01.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個ELEVEN…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.10,0:19:16.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吉爾弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候的白色機體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:31.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.30,0:19:33.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊  樞木准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.60,0:19:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三號攝像機怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是被ZERO拿走了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才想要反應啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.35,0:19:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道不是為此才拿走的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是為了要利用嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒能拯救成功
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,又一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:23.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  那個是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:26.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亞人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不必感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:31.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被困在酒店裡的人質我已全部救出
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.22,0:20:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,現在就讓他們回到你們的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.89,0:20:36.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.74,0:20:37.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.39,0:20:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然敢說如此厚顏無恥的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如果對你出手的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.27,0:20:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你會反過來利用人質吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.62,0:20:48.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敬畏我們 追隨我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的名字是  黑之騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,騎士團?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:20:57.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真諷刺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.49,0:21:00.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怖份子居然自稱騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們黑之騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是所有手無寸鐵之人的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.26,0:21:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:08.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還是布里塔尼亞人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.23,0:21:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,日本解放戰線
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:14.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,用卑劣的手段把布里塔尼亞平民當作人質
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.30,0:21:15.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,慘無人道地殺害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是無意義的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.95,0:21:20.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我們對此進行了制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.33,0:21:22.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:24.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼能停止放映
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.09,0:21:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,責任?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.13,0:21:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那種東西由我來承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.26,0:21:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,克洛維斯前總督也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.79,0:21:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下令虐殺手無寸鐵的ELEVEN
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我無法坐視這等殘暴的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.31,0:21:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此也對他進行了制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.00,0:21:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不否定戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.04,0:21:45.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,強者單方面虐殺弱者這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.29,0:21:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我絕不允許!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.27,0:21:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有資格開槍的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.85,0:21:51.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只有那些已有被殺覺悟的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.42,0:21:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,當擁有力量的強者欺凌沒有力量的弱者的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.43,0:21:56.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們將會再次出現
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.19,0:21:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,無論那個敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.69,0:22:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有多麼強大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.43,0:22:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正義的… 使者?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有力量的人們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.17,0:22:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,敬畏我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.48,0:22:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有力量的人們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.33,0:22:12.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,追隨我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.92,0:22:16.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,世界 將由我們黑之騎士團來…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.64,0:22:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,仲裁!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.73,0:23:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,運氣來臨了 天助我也
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.71,0:23:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到能抓住柯內莉婭的弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.98,0:23:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尤菲米婭這個弱點
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.07,0:24:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 現在開始就是黑之騎士團的…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.75,0:24:01.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也是我的反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.44,0:24:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向禁錮我的 這個世界
